{
  "name": "impulse_volume_breakout_v1_current90_sweep_v1",
  "description": "Research-first sweep for a new long family: high-volume 5m impulse breakout, then shallow retrace continuation entry. This is a different logic branch from the old 4h breakout-reclaim family.",
